# GRAPHICS::ANIMPOSTFX_IS_RUNNING

## Parameters
* **STRING** effectName: Returns true if the effect is active or fully faded in for effects that don't disable themselves at the end of their animation (eg: fade in effects), false otherwise

## Returns
* **BOOL**

## Notes
<!-- AUTOGENERATED: Remove this line before editing -->
Returns whether the specified effect is active.
See ANIMPOSTFX_PLAY

Full list of animpostFX / screen effects by DurtyFree: https://github.com/DurtyFree/gta-v-data-dumps/blob/master/animPostFxNamesCompact.json
